Several studies (
 Lancee et al., 2008; 
 Ji et al., 2017; 
 Xiao et al., 2020; 
 Wong et al., 2005; 
 Shih et al., 2007) identified a need for greater support through collaboration, training and education. This appeared to strengthen teams (
 Ji et al., 2017) and reduce HCW stress (
 Chua et al., 2004) as simple protective measures were reassuring for HCWs (
 Koh et al., 2005). Additionally, clear communication was seen to reduce psychiatric symptoms (
 Chan and Huak, 2004).
